            <p>Learn more about <a href="https://css-tricks.com/box-sizing/">box model and sizing at CSS Tricks</a>.</p>

            <h3 id="reboot">Reboot</h3>

            <p>For improved cross-browser rendering, we use <a href="/docs/4.3/content/reboot/">Reboot</a> to correct inconsistencies across browsers and devices while providing slightly more opinionated resets to common HTML elements.</p>

